3+ level example (categorical covariate, e.g. bad oil spill, moderate oil spill, no oil spill):

dummy &lt;- c(2, 1, 1, 3, 1)

In your model:

# Constraint
for(t in 1:Tmax){
  phi[t] &lt;- Mu.phi[dummy[t]]

}

# Priors
for(x in 1:3){
  Mu.phi[x] ~ dunif(0, 1)
}

